overview: How does Angela Summers do it? Not only is she official custodian and manager of a pair of America's classic chi-chis, but she has the time to share them with Boy Toy her new friend. Monique Hall is a statuesque work of art. Erica is a connoisseur of fine things and Monique's things are the finest she's ever seen. Rod likes tits big ones! Consequently, he loves Fawn Miller. If, big bouncing bobbing boons are bog on your list of likes you'll love Fawn Miller too and you'll love seeing her get the big one from Rod.
title: Breast Worx 18
